item.title: Congressman Pat Harrigan Takes on Foreign Threats and RNC Chairman Whatley Defends the Vote
item.description: This week on Breaking Battlegrounds, Congressman Pat Harrigan joins Chuck and Sam to discuss his new bill cracking down on foreign espionage from China, Russia, Iran, and North Korea, his national security wins in the NDAA, and why young Americans should consider joining the military. He also weighs in on U.S. support for Ukraine and removing Chinese influence from defense infrastructure... Feed: https://api.substack.com/feed/podcast/260675.rss
